interactivity.to_get_this_event: Win the lottery during A Life of Prizes . Autoplays after " A Life of Prizes " . This event belongs to an event chain started from " Wither " .
interactivity.to_miss_this_event: Finish A Life of Prizes without triggering it. Replaced by Ground Into Nothing .

changelog: This Event was added in Update 0.23p2.
